<li id="cite_note-9"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-9">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">M. I. Finley, ed. <i>The Portable Greek Historians: The Essence of Herodotus, Thucydides, Xenophon, Polybius</i> (1977) <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.amazon.com/The-Portable-Greek-Historians-Thucydides/dp/014015065X/ref=sr_1_1?s=books&ie=UTF8&qid=1331529320&sr=1-1">excerpt and text search</a></span></li>
